Notes: Cortland started the second half on a 21-0 run to take a 50-27 lead with 14:23
left. Oneonta rallied back within four points twice in the final minute.
Kristen Egan led Cortland with career highs of 15 points, 10 rebounds and
eight assists. Gabrielle Doemel scored 13 of 17 in the 2nd half for Oneonta.
Game.Officials: Mike Schmidt,  Owen Smith,  Dave Cusano
